group.diamonddev.internal

Class SpinedBuffer.OfPrimitive<E,T_ARR,T_CONS>

  • java.lang.Object
    • group.diamonddev.internal.SpinedBuffer.OfPrimitive<E,T_ARR,T_CONS>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpinedBuffer.OfDouble, SpinedBuffer.OfInt, SpinedBuffer.OfLong
    Enclosing class:
    SpinedBuffer

    abstract static class SpinedBuffer.OfPrimitive<E,T_ARR,T_CONS>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Base class for a data structure for gathering elements into a buffer and then iterating them. Maintains an array of increasingly sized arrays, so there is no copying cost associated with growing the data structure.
